TZ value in the original ones: TZ=MET+DST (without blanks).
At the moment we have some users that need to use TZ=   MET+DST and others
that need to use ZT=MET+DST.
Do you now something about this? 
We noted that the users who needed to chance TZ (from "   MET+DST" to
"MET+DST") had folders very big, about 400-500 Kbyte.
