You need a file named .forward in your home directory that looks something 
like this:

|/usr/local/bin/filter -q

And a file named .elm/filter-rules with rules like this:

if (from  fire-l@artopro.mlnet.com) then save ~/Mail/fire
if (from  rre-request@weber.ucsd.edu) then save ~/Mail/rre

The man pages for filter have some info in them and refer you to the Elm 
docs.

