On Sat, 19 Nov 1994, Terry Gray wrote:

> Having said that, and while agreeing with Mark and others that it would be
> better if those newsreaders that include the Newsgroups header in a *mail*
> message stopped doing so (or used a different header), there is one thing we
> can do in Pine to reduce the odds that someone will inadvertently post a msg
