You can set the time zone with the TZ environment variable.
set TZ=ZZZ[+H]H[:MM:SSTTT]
everything in [] is optional

ZZZ = time zone
+H = offset from GMT
TTT = daylight savings time

the default is PST-8PDT

i.e to set to EST
set TZ=EST-5EDT

cac.washington.edu has a file tech-notes which explains all this.


