You can also specify a folder-collection of

	*{imap.mid.net/anonymous}pub/NET/[]

to get the entire archive in a collection.  That way you can browse much more
easily.

Note that this syntax is specific to c-client based packages like Pine and
may be different on other IMAP clients.  The syntax will also change in a
future version of c-client/Pine... 

