of the screen?

Here is the program I was used:

#!/usr/bin/perl
$out_file = "jview_tmp.html";

open (JV, ">$out_file");

print JV "<html><body></pre>\n"; 

while (<>) {
	chop if m/\n$/;
	s/(http:\S+)/<a href=\"\1\">\1<\/a>/;
	s/(ftp:\S+)/<a href=\"\1\">\1<\/a>/;
	print JV $_, "\n";
}

print JV "</pre></body></html>\n"; 
close JV;

system ("lynx $out_file");


